ETHICAL USE NOTICE:

This software is designed for statistical analysis and research purposes to 
improve officiating consistency and transparency in floorball. Users are 
expected to:

1. Use the data responsibly and constructively
2. Focus on patterns and trends, not individual referee criticism
3. Respect the privacy and professionalism of referees
4. Not use the analysis for gambling, betting, or malicious purposes
5. Contribute to the positive development of the sport

The maintainers reserve the right to restrict access to users who violate 
these ethical guidelines.